  <section class="band faq">
    <div class="section-heading">
      <p class="eyebrow">Drain cleaning FAQ</p>
      <h2>Common questions before calling for drain cleaning</h2>
    </div>
    <details><summary>Do you provide drain cleaning in Brampton?</summary><p>Yes. Fateh Plumbing & Electric provides drain cleaning in Brampton for clogged sinks, toilets, tubs, floor drains, kitchen drains, main drains, and recurring backups.</p></details>
    <details><summary>When is a clogged drain an emergency?</summary><p>A clogged drain can be urgent if sewage is backing up, multiple fixtures are blocked, water is overflowing, or the home has no working toilet. In those cases, call the <a href="emergency-plumber.html">emergency plumber</a> page or phone number right away.</p></details>
    <details><summary>Can you clear a clogged toilet or kitchen sink?</summary><p>Yes. We help with clogged toilets, kitchen sink clogs, bathroom sink clogs, tub and shower drains, floor drains, and slow drains. Fixture-related problems can also connect to <a href="toilet-faucet-repair.html">toilet and faucet repair</a>.</p></details>
    <details><summary>Why does my drain keep clogging again?</summary><p>Recurring clogs can be caused by grease, hair, soap buildup, roots, damaged pipe, poor slope, or a blockage deeper in the main drain. If the clog keeps coming back, a <a href="sewer-camera-inspection.html">sewer camera inspection</a> may help identify the cause.</p></details>
    <details><summary>Do I need sewer line repair or drain cleaning?</summary><p>A single slow sink may only need drain cleaning. Multiple slow fixtures, basement backups, sewage smell, or recurring main drain clogs may need <a href="sewer-line-repair.html">sewer line repair</a>.</p></details>
    <details><summary>Should I use chemical drain cleaner first?</summary><p>Avoid chemical drain cleaners if the drain is fully blocked, overflowing, or backing up. They can sit in the pipe and make service more hazardous. Call for drain cleaning if the blockage does not clear safely.</p></details>
  </section>

